@startuml 订单异常处理流程
!include <C4/C4_Container>

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
    BorderColor #555555
}

' Colors
!define SERVICE_COLOR #E8F5E9
!define ENGINE_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define DB_COLOR #F3E5F5
!define EXT_COLOR #FCE4EC

title 订单异常处理 — HOLD / 超时关单 / 卡单检测 / 人工干预

' ========== 参与者 ==========

participant "原子服务\n(AtomicService)" as AtomicService #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "状态机引擎\n(StateMachineEngine)" as Engine #ENGINE_COLOR
participant "库存服务\n(InventoryService)" as Inventory #SERVICE_COLOR
collections "延迟任务\n(ADR-021)" as DelayedTask #SERVICE_COLOR
collections "卡单检测器\n(StuckDetector)" as Detector #SERVICE_COLOR
collections "退款对账\n(RefundReconcile)" as Reconcile #SERVICE_COLOR
database "订单DB\n(order)" as OrderDB #DB_COLOR
actor "客服\n(Admin)" as Admin #EXT_COLOR

' ========== 场景 1：库存不足 → HOLD ==========

== 场景 1：库存不足 → HOLD 挂起 ==

AtomicService -> Engine: transition(PENDING_PAY, HOLD, ctx)
activate Engine

Engine -> Engine: 守卫：库存不足
note right #FFCDD2
  Guard: InventoryAvailableCheck
  库存可用量 < 订单数量
  守卫返回 false → 拒绝 PAID 转换
  改为转入 HOLD 态
end note

Engine -> OrderDB: UPDATE status=HOLD,\nhold_reason='库存不足', version+=1
activate OrderDB
OrderDB --> Engine: ✅
deactivate Engine

Engine -> Engine: EntryAction: 注册 48h HOLD 超时告警任务
Engine --> AtomicService: ✅ HOLD

note right #FEFEFE
  HOLD 生命周期：
  ① 因库存不足/风控卡住
  ② 48h 内等待库存补充
  ③ 超时 → P2 告警
  ④ 库存恢复 → 自动解除
  ⑤ 商家放弃 → 取消订单
end note

' ========== 场景 2：HOLD 自动释放 ==========

== 场景 2：HOLD 自动释放 ==

actor "HoldReleaseJob\n(XXL-Job)" as HoldJob #SERVICE_COLOR

HoldJob -> HoldJob: 每隔 5 分钟扫描 HOLD 态订单
HoldJob -> Inventory: checkAvailability(orderId)
activate Inventory

alt 库存已补充
    Inventory --> HoldJob: ✅ available
    HoldJob -> Engine: transition(HOLD, PENDING_PAY, '库存补充')
    activate Engine
    Engine --> HoldJob: ✅ PENDING_PAY
    deactivate Engine
    note right #FEFEFE
      根据 previous_status 决定恢复目标：
      • PAID → HOLD → PAID
      • PENDING_PAY → HOLD → PENDING_PAY
    end note
else 仍不足
    Inventory --> HoldJob: ❌ unavailable
    HoldJob -> HoldJob: 跳过，下次再检
end

deactivate Inventory

' ========== 场景 3：支付超时自动关单 ==========

== 场景 3：支付超时自动关单 ==

participant "超时任务\n(PaymentTimeoutHandler)" as TimeoutHandler #SERVICE_COLOR

note right #FEFEFE
  触发：订单创建时注册 Tier 2
  RocketMQ 延迟消息（30 分钟）
end note

DelayedTask -> TimeoutHandler: 30min 超时触发
activate TimeoutHandler

TimeoutHandler -> OrderDB: 查询订单状态
activate OrderDB

alt 状态 = PENDING_PAY
    OrderDB --> TimeoutHandler: 未支付
    TimeoutHandler -> Engine: transition(PENDING_PAY, CLOSED, '超时')
    activate Engine
    Engine --> TimeoutHandler: ✅ CLOSED
    deactivate Engine
    note right #FEFEFE
      超时关单后置动作：
      • 释放预占库存
      • 释放优惠券锁定
      • 记录关单原因
    end note
else 状态 ≠ PENDING_PAY（已支付）
    OrderDB --> TimeoutHandler: 已支付
    TimeoutHandler -> TimeoutHandler: 跳过（订单已推进）
    note right #FEFEFE
      取消的支付超时任务：
      由于 RocketMQ 延迟消息不可取消，
      消费者自行判断状态已变更 → 跳过
    end note
end

deactivate OrderDB
deactivate TimeoutHandler

' ========== 场景 4：卡单检测器 ==========

== 场景 4：StuckOrderDetector 卡单检测 ==

actor "StuckOrderDetector\n(XXL-Job)" as DetectorJob #SERVICE_COLOR

DetectorJob -> DetectorJob: 每隔 5 分钟扫描所有非终态订单
DetectorJob -> OrderDB: SELECT * FROM order\nWHERE status_expires_at < NOW()\nAND status NOT IN (COMPLETED,...)

loop 每个卡单
    DetectorJob -> DetectorJob: 按超时矩阵配置处理
    note right #FEFEFE
      超时矩阵（Apollo 配置驱动）：
      TO_SHIP > 72h → P2 告警
      REFUNDING > 72h → 触发退款对账
      HOLD > 48h → P2 告警
    end note

    DetectorJob -> Engine: 触发预设处理
    note right #FEFEFE
      处理策略：
      • AUTO_CLOSE → 自动关单
      • AUTO_CONFIRM → 自动确认
      • RECONCILE → 触发对账
      • ALERT_ONLY → 仅告警
    end note
end

' ========== 场景 5：退款对账 ==========

== 场景 5：退款状态对账 ==

actor "RefundReconcileJob\n(XXL-Job)" as ReconcileJob #SERVICE_COLOR
actor "支付网关\n(PaymentGateway)" as PaymentGateway #EXT_COLOR

ReconcileJob -> ReconcileJob: 每隔 30 分钟扫描卡在 REFUNDING/RETURNING 的订单
ReconcileJob -> OrderDB: SELECT * FROM order\nWHERE status IN (REFUNDING, RETURNING)\nAND status_expires_at < NOW()
ReconcileJob -> PaymentGateway: queryRefundStatus(txId)
activate PaymentGateway

alt 支付网关退款成功
    PaymentGateway --> ReconcileJob: SUCCESS
    ReconcileJob -> Engine: transition(REFUNDING, REFUNDED, '对账完成')
    activate Engine
    Engine --> ReconcileJob: ✅ REFUNDED
    deactivate Engine
else 支付网关退款失败
    PaymentGateway --> ReconcileJob: FAILED
    ReconcileJob -> ReconcileJob: P1 告警：退款异常
    note right #FFCDD2
      告警信息：
      订单 XXX 支付网关退款失败
      需要人工介入处理
    end note
else 仍处理中
    PaymentGateway --> ReconcileJob: PENDING
    ReconcileJob -> ReconcileJob: 跳过，下次再检
end
deactivate PaymentGateway

' ========== 场景 6：人工干预 ==========

== 场景 6：人工干预 API ==

Admin -> Admin: 客服通过工作台查看卡单列表
Admin -> Engine: GET /api/admin/v1/orders/stuck?status=TO_SHIP

note right #FEFEFE
  返回值：卡单详情
  • 订单号 / 当前状态
  • 停留时长 / 超时时间
  • 最后一次操作记录
  • 建议操作按钮
end note

Admin -> Engine: POST /api/admin/v1/orders/{no}/freeze\n{reason: "商家长时间不发货"}
activate Engine
Engine -> OrderDB: UPDATE status=FROZEN,\nfrozen_reason='商家长时间不发货'
OrderDB --> Engine: ✅
Engine --> Admin: ✅
note right #FEFEFE
  冻结效果：
  • 所有自动任务跳过此订单
  • 买家可见"订单已冻结，联系客服"
  • 解冻后恢复原状态
end note
deactivate Engine

Admin -> Engine: POST /api/admin/v1/orders/{no}/unfreeze
activate Engine
Engine -> OrderDB: UPDATE status=TO_SHIP\n(恢复冻结前状态)
OrderDB --> Engine: ✅
Engine --> Admin: ✅
deactivate Engine

note right #FEFEFE
  人工干预 API 清单：
  • freeze — 冻结
  • unfreeze — 解冻
  • force-transition（SUPER_ADMIN）
    — 强制转换（跳过守卫）
  • stuck — 查询卡单列表
  所有操作记录审计日志
end note

@enduml
